{
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "──星期四。第5周的早晨。\n与奈奈的关系加深了,治疗也变得更加大胆。而且幸运的是,店铺的经营状况也有了变化……"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "(已经第5周了……最近一点一点地有新客人来了。)"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "(昨天来了3个,前天2个……大家都异口同声地说\"是朋友介绍来的\"。)"
    },
    {
      "include": "common/weekly_settlement"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "",
      "playSE": "door_chime"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_smile_openmouth",
      "text": "早上好!今天也请多关照。",
      "voiceFile": "story_day5_001"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal_smile",
      "text": "早上好,奈奈。其实我想谢谢你。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_openmouth",
      "text": "谢我……为什么?",
      "voiceFile": "story_day5_002"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal_smile",
      "text": "最近新客人增加了。大家都说\"是朋友介绍的\",我相信你一定为我宣传了店铺。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_smile_openmouth",
      "text": "哦……是的。我告诉朋友们的时候,大家都很感兴趣……",
      "voiceFile": "story_day5_003"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_happysmile",
      "text": "我真的很喜欢这里的按摩……所以想让大家也体验一下。",
      "voiceFile": "story_day5_004"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal_smile",
      "text": "非常感谢。多亏了你,我觉得这家店能继续经营下去了。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_nervoussmile",
      "text": "哪里……我只是觉得好才说的……",
      "voiceFile": "story_day5_005"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "不过……那套特殊的衣服有点难解释……",
      "voiceFile": "story_day5_006"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "哈哈哈,我想也是。但你看起来已经很习惯了。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_nervoussmile",
      "text": "嗯……一开始很害羞,但现在已经觉得是治疗的一部分了。",
      "voiceFile": "story_day5_007"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal_closemouth",
      "text": "那么,今天感觉怎么样?"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "其实……最近身体变得非常敏感……",
      "voiceFile": "story_day5_008"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "即使只是轻轻触碰也会吓一跳……",
      "voiceFile": "story_day5_009"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "这是血液循环改善、神经变得活跃的证据。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "是这样吗……但感觉很奇怪……",
      "voiceFile": "story_day5_010"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "特别是……胸部和腹部……感觉很麻……",
      "voiceFile": "story_day5_011"
    },
    {
      "id": "choice_massage5",
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "我明白了……这是你的身体正在变化的证据。",
      "choices": [
        {
          "label": "这是健康的反应",
          "trustDelta": 2,
          "developDelta": 0,
          "next": "healthy_path"
