    {
      "id": "healthy_path",
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_smile",
      "text": "健康的反应……这样啊。那就放心了。",
      "voiceFile": "story_day5_012"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal_closemouth",
      "text": "是的。这证明你的身体正常运作,不用担心。",
      "next": "change_clothes"
    },
    {
      "id": "hormone_path",
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_surprised_sweat",
      "text": "女-女性荷尔蒙……是说?",
      "voiceFile": "story_day5_013"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "是的。按摩改善血液循环时,荷尔蒙平衡也会得到调节。这意味着你变得更有女人味了。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "更有女人味……这么说来,最近皮肤状况也变好了……",
      "next": "change_clothes",
