    {
      "id": "change_clothes",
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal_closemouth",
      "text": "那么,今天也请换衣服吧。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_smile_openmouth",
      "text": "好的。我已经相当习惯了。",
      "voiceFile": "story_day5_017"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_closeeyes_closemouth",
      "text": "(但是……最近穿上这套衣服的时候,心跳会加速……)",
